Run the application:

    $ ./gradlew run

Send GET requests:

    $ curl http://localhost:8080/math/doMath/4/7
      {"x":4,"y":7,"product":28,"sum":11}

    $ curl http://localhost:8080/math/doMath/7/2
      {"x":7,"y":2,"product":14,"sum":9}

Build an executable jar:

    $ ./gradlew assemble
    $ java -jar build/libs/micromath-0.2-all.jar
    16:44:13.644 [main] INFO  io.micronaut.runtime.Micronaut - Startup completed in 1030ms. Server Running: http://localhost:8080
